386→                        <div id="content">Let $G$ be a graph with $1+n(m-1)$ vertices and $1+n\binom{m}{2}$ edges. Must $G$ contain two points which are connected by $m$ disjoint paths?</div>
387→                        <div id="problem_id"><a href="/915">#915</a>: <a href="#cite-BoEr62-915" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('BoEr62','915'); return false;">[BoEr62]</a><a href="#cite-Er67b-915" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er67b','915'); return false;">[Er67b,p.4]</a></div>
